 <title>Anatomy tool</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/co-design/tools/anatomy-tool</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;Defining roles and responsibilities of people delivering services. &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-tool-stages field--type-taxonomy-term-reference field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;At what stage of the design process is the tool most useful?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/category/design-stages/define&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Define&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-tool-what field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The anatomy tool helps the co-design team think about the attributes, roles and responsibilities of the people delivering the service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-tool-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How do you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Encourage the group to consider all of the people who deliver the service. (There are likely to be different groups of people).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For each group of people who deliver the service, encourage the co-design team to pick four key attributes and describe a situation where they might need them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-tool-useful field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Useful resources when using the tool&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;In Pilotlight we used this tool to co-design &lt;a href=&quot;https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/blog/peer-support-values-and-skills-self-directed-support&quot;&gt;SDS peer worker &lt;/a&gt;and reablement worker roles. It has been suggested that this tool could be used to support personal assistant job design and recruitment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
